1
00:01:32,040 --> 00:01:32,640
If not for you,

2
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:33,920
we'd be together already!

3
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:36,920
Chen Xuanqing, you're out of your mind.

4
00:01:37,159 --> 00:01:38,040
I am!

5
00:01:43,359 --> 00:01:44,359
The moment I learned

6
00:01:45,239 --> 00:01:46,359
you were going to marry him,

7
00:01:46,359 --> 00:01:47,519
I've already lost my mind.

8
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,239
Chen Yanyun,

9
00:01:52,359 --> 00:01:53,760
you sit high above

10
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,359
with immense power,

11
00:01:56,959 --> 00:01:59,079
but you're nothing but a hypocrite.

12
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:01,120
You made me one of the Chen

13
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:02,920
because you pitied me.

14
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:04,640
But in fact, all you want from me

15
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,920
is my future to serve your clan!

16
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:08,159
You can't stand to see me soar.

17
00:02:08,439 --> 00:02:10,000
You manipulate and control me.

18
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:14,000
You knew Jinzhao and I loved each other,

19
00:02:14,439 --> 00:02:15,680
yet you deliberately betrothed me

20
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:16,520
to the Yu family.

21
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:19,159
You talk about worrying

22
00:02:19,159 --> 00:02:20,080
for my future.

23
00:02:20,639 --> 00:02:21,479
But all of this is

24
00:02:21,479 --> 00:02:22,800
just to take Jinzhao from me!

25
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,240
You're talking nonsense.

26
00:02:30,319 --> 00:02:32,240
These are just in your imagination.

27
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:33,479
Really?

28
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,039
My imagination?

29
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,479
Wake up from his spell!

30
00:02:43,639 --> 00:02:44,439
Are you really going
to deny you ever liked me?

31
00:02:46,479 --> 00:02:47,319
You went to great lengths

32
00:02:47,759 --> 00:02:48,479
to approach me

33
00:02:48,479 --> 00:02:49,800
at the academy.

34
00:02:50,319 --> 00:02:51,400
Even when Ye Xian beat you,

35
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,360
you endured it.

36
00:02:53,599 --> 00:02:54,400
I've seen all
your letters to me.

37
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,319
I wrote:

38
00:02:56,639 --> 00:02:57,840
"A roaming heart has a hundred thoughts;

39
00:02:58,439 --> 00:02:59,520
a thousand miles I wander alone."

40
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:01,759
You said you felt
the same, and told me not

41
00:03:02,759 --> 00:03:03,879
to be so melancholy.

42
00:03:04,919 --> 00:03:05,479
You understand

43
00:03:05,479 --> 00:03:06,840
me so well. Isn't that love?

44
00:03:14,039 --> 00:03:15,080
I was also there that day

45
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,560
on the bridge.

46
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:18,719
I also saw the kite

47
00:03:18,719 --> 00:03:19,599
you flew for me.

48
00:03:19,759 --> 00:03:20,439
You know what?

49
00:03:22,039 --> 00:03:23,000
You're too naive,

50
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,960
that's why he fooled you.

51
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,199
He's always played power games

52
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:28,240
and controlled hearts.

53
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,319
What you see

54
00:03:29,319 --> 00:03:30,439
is just what he wants you to see!

55
00:03:30,439 --> 00:03:31,479
Shut up!

56
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,120
I kill you!

57
00:03:36,159 --> 00:03:37,080
Yanyun! Yanyun!

58
00:03:37,719 --> 00:03:38,639
- Yanyun!
- Let go!

59
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,680
Yanyun!

60
00:04:00,759 --> 00:04:01,520
Throw him out!

61
00:04:02,159 --> 00:04:02,599
Yes, sir.

62
00:04:24,639 --> 00:04:25,920
I did nothing wrong!

63
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:26,639
Get up!

64
00:04:34,639 --> 00:04:36,279
Don't take out your anger on me

65
00:04:36,439 --> 00:04:37,360
because of my past.

66
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:06,720
I wish I could stay calm,

67
00:05:07,439 --> 00:05:08,000
but

68
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:12,319
I just can't right now.

69
00:05:24,959 --> 00:05:26,040
Leave me alone.

70
00:05:31,279 --> 00:05:32,160
Chen Yanyun!

71
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,560
If you leave now,

72
00:05:34,399 --> 00:05:35,560
don't ever come back!

73
00:06:04,319 --> 00:06:05,519
Is that true?

74
00:06:06,839 --> 00:06:08,160
How could I know?

75
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,680
I only heard it from my son.

76
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,519
He said his wife

77
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,800
came back from the Chen house

78
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:13,839
a changed woman,

79
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,240
kept claiming

80
00:06:16,639 --> 00:06:17,519
Chen Yanyun

81
00:06:17,639 --> 00:06:19,240
will avenge her father.

82
00:06:19,639 --> 00:06:21,439
But where would he get the evidence?

83
00:06:22,759 --> 00:06:24,000
When I executed Yanhong,

84
00:06:24,279 --> 00:06:26,120
I was as careful as could be.

85
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,240
In any case,

86
00:06:33,079 --> 00:06:34,680
you'd better plan ahead.

87
00:06:35,439 --> 00:06:36,680
This is no small matter.

88
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:38,399
If it ever comes to light,

89
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,680
all your grand ambitions

90
00:06:41,079 --> 00:06:42,560
will be wasted.

91
00:06:43,439 --> 00:06:44,560
What are you saying?

92
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:46,360
If he falls,

93
00:06:46,639 --> 00:06:48,160
what good does that do you?

94
00:06:50,639 --> 00:06:51,720
Why are you stopping me?

95
00:06:55,079 --> 00:06:56,720
Chen Yanyun has known about Yanhong.

96
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:57,560
What?

97
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,040
Who?

98
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,360
The woman

99
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:02,040
sent by Prince Chengqing back then.

100
00:07:02,959 --> 00:07:04,399
Wasn't she thrown into the river?

101
00:07:05,279 --> 00:07:06,319
After all these years,

102
00:07:06,319 --> 00:07:07,120
how could they know?

103
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,519
I don't know!

104
00:07:09,279 --> 00:07:10,560
It's terrifying.

105
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:11,639
What,

106
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:12,639
what,

107
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,800
what are we going to do?

108
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:17,759
Calm down.

109
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,600
I wasn't the only one colluding

110
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,720
with Prince Chengqing.

111
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,319
Even if they uncover something,

112
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,680
the Lord Chief Councilor knows me.

113
00:07:27,079 --> 00:07:28,360
If it really comes to that,

114
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,639
I

115
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:32,800
am not afraid to burn it all down.

116
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:38,199
Servant!

117
00:07:40,279 --> 00:07:40,800
Sir.

118
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,560
Keep a close watch on Chen Yanyun.

119
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,000
Report any sign of his movement

120
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:44,759
immediately.

121
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:45,560
Yes, sir.
Also,

122
00:07:47,839 --> 00:07:49,160
we suspected before that he once

123
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,319
colluded with the waterway bandits.

124
00:07:50,639 --> 00:07:51,399
Look into that

125
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,639
thoroughly again.

126
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,199
And that Chen Xuanqing.

127
00:07:54,839 --> 00:07:55,560
I recall he was

128
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:56,600
adopted from Xuzhou
Prefecture.

129
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,800
He could very well be linked to the bandits.

130
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,519
Investigate him thoroughly,

131
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:01,600
doing everything you can.

132
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:03,079
Dig up hard evidence.

133
00:08:03,759 --> 00:08:04,279
Yes, sir.

134
00:10:00,519 --> 00:10:01,159
Quick, Mr. Jiang.

135
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:02,480
Quick!
Quick, Mr. Jiang.

136
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,240
What happened to Mr. Chen?
You should have seen him!

137
00:10:05,399 --> 00:10:06,240
Something's really wrong!

138
00:10:06,799 --> 00:10:07,279
How?
I can't describe it.

139
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:09,200
Just go and see for yourself!

140
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:10,759
Go!

141
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:11,799
Be quick!

142
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:13,519
Slow down!

143
00:10:13,519 --> 00:10:14,840
Sir, here comes Mr. Jiang.

144
00:10:17,639 --> 00:10:18,960
Sir, you...

145
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:28,399
Sir.

146
00:10:30,039 --> 00:10:31,120
Just as expected,

147
00:10:31,639 --> 00:10:32,720
Wang Xuanfan is making moves.

148
00:10:32,919 --> 00:10:33,919
He's not only got men
tailing you,

149
00:10:35,039 --> 00:10:36,559
but he's also made contact with

150
00:10:36,919 --> 00:10:37,759
the bandits in Zhending.

151
00:10:43,519 --> 00:10:44,559
Go on.

152
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,080
Normally,

153
00:10:50,879 --> 00:10:51,600
our plan

154
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:52,840
can proceed as is.

155
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:53,799
But if you

156
00:10:55,279 --> 00:10:56,240
want to take it slower...

157
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,240
No.

158
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,480
Proceed as we planned.

159
00:11:00,679 --> 00:11:01,120
Okay.

160
00:11:07,559 --> 00:11:09,000
By the way,

161
00:11:09,279 --> 00:11:10,360
Qingpu

162
00:11:10,679 --> 00:11:11,559
came to me.

163
00:11:14,759 --> 00:11:15,679
What did she want?

164
00:11:16,399 --> 00:11:17,639
She said

165
00:11:18,159 --> 00:11:20,000
you may need to come back and see the madame.

166
00:11:20,399 --> 00:11:21,000
Madame has been

167
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,879
waiting for you all day,

168
00:11:23,279 --> 00:11:24,279
without meals

169
00:11:24,519 --> 00:11:25,519
nor sleeping.

170
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,519
She wouldn't do that

171
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:35,399
for my sake.

172
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:37,279
You haven't gone back.

173
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:37,799
How,
how would you know?

174
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,240
I know I shouldn't

175
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,279
speak out of turn,

176
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,159
but this really

177
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:44,919
isn't her fault.

178
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:46,440
These days, she's been

179
00:11:46,879 --> 00:11:47,960
avoiding Xuanqing

180
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:48,919
whenever possible.

181
00:11:49,799 --> 00:11:51,240
It's Chen Xuanqing who...

182
00:11:52,279 --> 00:11:53,559
Forcing her,

183
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:54,919
right?

184
00:11:58,159 --> 00:11:58,759
Yes.

185
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:12,919
Sir,

186
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:14,399
sir,

187
00:12:15,559 --> 00:12:17,080
say something, please!

188
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:19,399
I,

189
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:21,000
I pour you some water.

190
00:12:43,159 --> 00:12:44,480
I've written to the Yu family.

191
00:12:44,879 --> 00:12:45,840
Your engagement
to Wanxue is canceled.

192
00:12:49,039 --> 00:12:49,759
You'll to be posted out.

193
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:53,320
You can't,

194
00:12:58,600 --> 00:12:59,440
you can't do this!

195
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:02,639
I earned the first place in exam.

196
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:07,039
You can't send me to an outward post!

197
00:13:08,279 --> 00:13:09,480
If I hadn't been there today,

198
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:11,639
with your

199
00:13:11,639 --> 00:13:12,600
extreme nature,

200
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:13,759
Jinzhao's

201
00:13:14,279 --> 00:13:15,639
reputation would have been ruined.

202
00:13:16,559 --> 00:13:18,120
Our family would have been disgraced as well.

203
00:13:19,039 --> 00:13:19,919
I won't let you stay
in the capital any longer.

204
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,519
Go to the provinces.

205
00:13:23,039 --> 00:13:23,919
If you can settle down

206
00:13:24,600 --> 00:13:25,960
and be a solid official,

207
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,559
perhaps I'll think better of you.

208
00:13:33,799 --> 00:13:34,399
Uncle Yanyun.

209
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:35,559
Uncle Yanyun.

210
00:13:36,279 --> 00:13:36,799
I was wrong.

211
00:13:37,759 --> 00:13:39,000
I was truly wrong, Uncle Yanyun.

212
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:43,399
Uncle Yanyun.

213
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:48,240
I've studied for years.

214
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:51,440
I earned the title of Jinshi

215
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:52,919
and my place in Hanlin Academy.

216
00:13:53,279 --> 00:13:54,919
His Highness also favors me.

217
00:13:55,639 --> 00:13:56,200
Uncle Yanyun!

218
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:58,519
Uncle Yanyun!

219
00:13:59,039 --> 00:14:00,159
You can't send me to the provinces!

220
00:14:01,559 --> 00:14:02,200
Uncle Yanyun!

221
00:14:04,799 --> 00:14:05,759
Wang Xuanfan

222
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:08,519
is already looking into your birth father.

223
00:14:09,159 --> 00:14:10,320
Sending you away

224
00:14:10,519 --> 00:14:11,679
is for your own good.

225
00:14:13,159 --> 00:14:14,200
Take care of yourself.

226
00:14:23,759 --> 00:14:24,200
Sir!

227
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:26,919
Sir!

228
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:30,320
Sir!
Sir!

229
00:14:42,519 --> 00:14:44,159
Why does Yanyun have to act like this?

230
00:14:44,559 --> 00:14:45,879
He clearly cares deeply for his wife,

231
00:14:46,120 --> 00:14:47,360
yet insists on being stubborn.

232
00:14:47,600 --> 00:14:48,279
Besides,
this truly

233
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,240
isn't her fault.

234
00:14:50,360 --> 00:14:51,720
it's all Chen Xuanqing's doing.

235
00:14:51,919 --> 00:14:52,759
It's all over,

236
00:14:52,879 --> 00:14:54,000
yet he had to dig it up.

237
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:56,039
You think Yanyun

238
00:14:56,039 --> 00:14:57,399
doesn't know she's innocent?

239
00:14:58,039 --> 00:14:58,840
He just

240
00:14:58,840 --> 00:15:00,200
can't get past it himself.

241
00:15:00,879 --> 00:15:01,919
What do you mean?

242
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:06,559
Think about it.

243
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:08,159
Through all his years:

244
00:15:08,559 --> 00:15:11,000
the treacherous courts,

245
00:15:11,399 --> 00:15:13,360
the bitter trials of the world outside.

246
00:15:13,799 --> 00:15:15,279
He's weathered countless storms.

247
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:19,159
Yet this matter of love is his first,

248
00:15:19,279 --> 00:15:21,000
utterly unfamiliar.

249
00:15:21,919 --> 00:15:23,639
And love is the one thing

250
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:25,320
that defies

251
00:15:25,320 --> 00:15:26,480
clear reasoning.

252
00:15:27,679 --> 00:15:29,000
Add to that

253
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:30,679
his pride and his inward,

254
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:32,879
reserved nature—

255
00:15:33,159 --> 00:15:34,039
no wonder he's tied

256
00:15:34,240 --> 00:15:34,960
himself in knots.

257
00:15:39,240 --> 00:15:39,919
I didn't get it.

258
00:15:45,799 --> 00:15:47,000
Just remember,

259
00:15:47,159 --> 00:15:48,759
his staying away right now

260
00:15:49,240 --> 00:15:50,919
also spares his wife worry.

261
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:52,200
After all,

262
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:54,080
this plan

263
00:15:54,279 --> 00:15:56,679
hides even from her.

264
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:10,559
It's been days.

265
00:16:10,960 --> 00:16:12,799
Why hasn't Yanyun returned yet?

266
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:16,679
Stop the gossip.

267
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:19,759
I hear you caught a chill a few days ago.

268
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:22,960
You still look pale.

269
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:24,919
You should be resting at home.

270
00:16:25,240 --> 00:16:26,320
Why come all the way here?

271
00:16:27,879 --> 00:16:28,960
Some things

272
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:31,480
need to be settled sooner.

273
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:34,039
Here is

274
00:16:34,559 --> 00:16:35,519
better than at home.

275
00:16:39,120 --> 00:16:40,080
Jinzhao.

276
00:16:42,960 --> 00:16:44,240
What on earth happened?

277
00:16:44,399 --> 00:16:46,000
Why the sudden decision to break off the engagement?

278
00:16:56,799 --> 00:16:57,320
Take a seat.

279
00:17:02,799 --> 00:17:03,559
What did

280
00:17:04,279 --> 00:17:05,440
Mr. Yu tell you?

281
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:07,680
My father only said the engagement

282
00:17:07,960 --> 00:17:08,720
was off,

283
00:17:09,119 --> 00:17:10,440
not another word.

284
00:17:11,480 --> 00:17:13,000
I went to see Xuanqing,

285
00:17:13,440 --> 00:17:14,559
but he refused to see me.

286
00:17:15,119 --> 00:17:16,480
Father found out that

287
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:17,599
and scolded me,

288
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:19,920
forbidding me to see Xuanqing again.

289
00:17:20,319 --> 00:17:21,960
If you hadn't sent someone to me today,

290
00:17:22,559 --> 00:17:24,240
father wouldn't even let me leave the house.

291
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:26,839
I asked you here today

292
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:28,680
to explain it clearly

293
00:17:28,880 --> 00:17:30,559
to you in person.

294
00:17:31,440 --> 00:17:32,839
You heard what

295
00:17:33,039 --> 00:17:34,359
Xuanqing said that day

296
00:17:34,680 --> 00:17:35,640
at Lan's place.

297
00:17:37,079 --> 00:17:37,960
After weighing
the pros and cons,

298
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:40,519
Yanyun, your father, and I

299
00:17:41,680 --> 00:17:42,880
all agree that you and Xuanqing

300
00:17:43,440 --> 00:17:44,400
are not a good match.

301
00:17:51,240 --> 00:17:52,200
It's you.

302
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:55,079
You're the one Xuanqing has in his heart,

303
00:17:55,839 --> 00:17:57,119
aren't you?

304
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:09,680
I've actually suspected it for a long time.

305
00:18:11,599 --> 00:18:12,759
That day, Xuanqing

306
00:18:12,920 --> 00:18:14,559
seemed to be talking to me,

307
00:18:16,880 --> 00:18:18,880
but he was clearly staring at you the whole time.

308
00:18:20,880 --> 00:18:21,839
I knew then that

309
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:25,279
he wasn't being honest with me.

310
00:18:26,759 --> 00:18:27,880
He was using me to show

311
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:29,440
his feelings for you.

312
00:18:30,680 --> 00:18:31,960
That's why the engagement must be canceled.

313
00:18:32,880 --> 00:18:33,599
Wanxue,

314
00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:35,480
you should find someone

315
00:18:35,480 --> 00:18:37,160
who knows, understands, and truly

316
00:18:37,519 --> 00:18:38,200
loves you.

317
00:18:38,279 --> 00:18:39,319
What's the use

318
00:18:39,319 --> 00:18:40,240
of these words now?

319
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:43,640
I told you

320
00:18:44,400 --> 00:18:46,480
I've had feelings for Xuanqing since I was little.

321
00:18:47,039 --> 00:18:47,839
I said I'm willing

322
00:18:48,119 --> 00:18:48,920
to marry him

323
00:18:48,920 --> 00:18:50,119
no matter what.

324
00:18:50,880 --> 00:18:51,680
And you've

325
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:52,920
already married Uncle Yanyun.

326
00:18:53,480 --> 00:18:54,240
Why must you

327
00:18:54,240 --> 00:18:55,680
expose everything?

328
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:58,240
Couldn't we just live

329
00:18:58,920 --> 00:18:59,839
our separate lives?

330
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:01,480
You cannot
knowingly

331
00:19:02,920 --> 00:19:04,319
jump into a fire pit!

332
00:19:08,319 --> 00:19:09,839
Do you still have feelings for Xuanqing?

333
00:19:10,200 --> 00:19:11,000
Of course not.

334
00:19:11,559 --> 00:19:12,279
Then could you

335
00:19:12,279 --> 00:19:13,319
ask Uncle Yanyun

336
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:15,039
not to cancel the engagement?

337
00:19:15,240 --> 00:19:15,839
No.

338
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:18,480
Xuanqing will soon

339
00:19:18,720 --> 00:19:19,559
take a post outside

340
00:19:19,880 --> 00:19:20,920
the capital and never return.

341
00:19:22,599 --> 00:19:23,359
Forget about him.

342
00:19:48,799 --> 00:19:49,599
[Will you]

343
00:19:50,640 --> 00:19:51,680
[stay with me?]

344
00:19:52,799 --> 00:19:53,839
[When trouble comes,]

345
00:19:54,519 --> 00:19:56,079
[don't shrink back right away.]

346
00:19:57,240 --> 00:19:58,039
[Let's see if we can]

347
00:19:58,279 --> 00:19:59,920
[find a better way]

348
00:20:00,559 --> 00:20:01,240
[to solve it.]

349
00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:03,640
[You once said]

350
00:20:04,240 --> 00:20:05,480
[we'd face it together,]

351
00:20:05,640 --> 00:20:06,680
[solve it together.]

352
00:20:07,799 --> 00:20:08,799
[And now?]

353
00:20:16,799 --> 00:20:18,519
[I wish I could stay calm,]

354
00:20:19,319 --> 00:20:20,000
[but...]

355
00:20:39,960 --> 00:20:41,400
[You keep avoiding me]

356
00:20:41,680 --> 00:20:42,519
[like this.]

357
00:20:43,839 --> 00:20:45,680
[Now I'll force you once,]

358
00:20:46,599 --> 00:20:48,599
[just to see if you truly decide]

359
00:20:48,880 --> 00:20:50,039
[to never turn back.]

360
00:21:31,119 --> 00:21:32,000
Take this

361
00:21:33,440 --> 00:21:34,400
to Chen Yi

362
00:21:35,039 --> 00:21:36,079
and have him pass it to Yanyun.

363
00:21:37,960 --> 00:21:38,559
Miss,

364
00:21:39,400 --> 00:21:40,440
it doesn't have to come to that.

365
00:21:41,079 --> 00:21:42,039
Why not wait a little?

366
00:21:42,960 --> 00:21:43,759
I've waited

367
00:21:44,119 --> 00:21:45,319
plenty of days.

368
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:46,839
I don't want to wait anymore.

369
00:21:48,680 --> 00:21:49,799
He knows I've done

370
00:21:50,079 --> 00:21:50,880
nothing wrong,

371
00:21:51,680 --> 00:21:53,160
yet he keeps making things difficult.

372
00:21:54,079 --> 00:21:55,319
I'm not going to put up with it.

373
00:21:58,799 --> 00:21:59,559
Yes, miss.

374
00:22:22,680 --> 00:22:23,240
Sir.

375
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:25,720
Is everything ready?
Yes.

376
00:22:26,680 --> 00:22:27,160
Let's go.

377
00:22:28,240 --> 00:22:28,799
Right, sir.

378
00:22:29,160 --> 00:22:30,119
Qingpu brought this.

379
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:31,279
A letter from Madam.

380
00:22:31,599 --> 00:22:32,119
Madam?
Yes.

381
00:25:01,279 --> 00:25:02,759
Jinzhao is resourceful. She actually

382
00:25:03,039 --> 00:25:04,160
managed to invite Grand

383
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:04,920
Secretaries' womenfolk.

384
00:25:05,279 --> 00:25:07,079
We won't have to worry about business from now on.

385
00:25:08,720 --> 00:25:10,279
I'm not worried about the business.

386
00:25:10,720 --> 00:25:12,079
I'm worried about Jinzhao.

387
00:25:25,440 --> 00:25:26,559
This tea smells wonderful.

388
00:25:27,200 --> 00:25:28,200
It's this year's

389
00:25:28,279 --> 00:25:29,359
first-picked Songluo tea,

390
00:25:29,640 --> 00:25:31,119
brewed with mountain spring water.

391
00:25:35,200 --> 00:25:36,920
This pattern leaves room for adjustment, ma'am.

392
00:25:37,200 --> 00:25:38,319
You can cut the fabric together

393
00:25:38,319 --> 00:25:40,119
with the outer edge of the pattern.

394
00:25:40,920 --> 00:25:41,640
Do you really think

395
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:42,880
I don't know to cut it?

396
00:25:43,920 --> 00:25:44,720
Well,

397
00:25:44,960 --> 00:25:46,359
it's just a piece of fabric.

398
00:25:46,559 --> 00:25:48,200
If it's ruined, it's ruined.

399
00:25:49,039 --> 00:25:50,599
What do you mean by that?

400
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:51,559
Are you saying

401
00:25:51,559 --> 00:25:52,720
I ruined it on purpose?

402
00:25:53,200 --> 00:25:53,599
I...

403
00:25:54,119 --> 00:25:55,519
We are cutting fabric

404
00:25:55,920 --> 00:25:58,240
to emulate the Empress Dowager's example

405
00:25:58,799 --> 00:26:00,720
of encouraging mulberry cultivation among the people.

406
00:26:01,640 --> 00:26:03,680
But if too much fabric is ruined,

407
00:26:04,039 --> 00:26:06,319
it loses its original meaning.

408
00:26:10,279 --> 00:26:11,480
I have an idea.

409
00:26:12,720 --> 00:26:13,839
Keep the ruined

410
00:26:14,079 --> 00:26:14,839
pieces and have them

411
00:26:15,440 --> 00:26:17,000
sewn together into a patchwork cloth,

412
00:26:17,640 --> 00:26:18,759
make a hundred-family garment,

413
00:26:19,079 --> 00:26:20,519
and donate it to the orphanage.

414
00:26:21,359 --> 00:26:22,799
What a wonderful idea!

415
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:26,000
Mrs. Chen is so clever.

416
00:26:26,319 --> 00:26:27,160
This approach

417
00:26:27,480 --> 00:26:29,440
will ease our mind.

418
00:26:31,119 --> 00:26:32,200
I'd say,

419
00:26:32,880 --> 00:26:35,160
Mrs. Chen's cleverness comes second.

420
00:26:35,720 --> 00:26:38,279
What truly matters is her magnanimity.

421
00:26:39,000 --> 00:26:40,240
With her uncle

422
00:26:40,599 --> 00:26:42,319
dismissed and half the family's property

423
00:26:42,960 --> 00:26:44,880
confiscated, whoever in her shoes

424
00:26:45,200 --> 00:26:46,599
would have already cried out their eyes.

425
00:26:47,079 --> 00:26:48,119
But Mrs. Chen

426
00:26:48,440 --> 00:26:50,000
remains perfectly calm,

427
00:26:50,160 --> 00:26:51,680
still sitting here, drinking tea.

428
00:26:55,599 --> 00:26:57,440
He broke the law and deserves

429
00:26:57,759 --> 00:26:58,599
his punishment.

430
00:26:59,279 --> 00:27:00,319
What reason do I have to cry?

431
00:27:02,160 --> 00:27:03,480
Well said.

432
00:27:03,839 --> 00:27:04,880
No wonder Mrs. Chen

433
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:06,119
has seen her share of trials.

434
00:27:07,039 --> 00:27:08,039
I heard that

435
00:27:08,440 --> 00:27:09,799
the reason Mrs. Chen was sent

436
00:27:09,920 --> 00:27:11,680
to her maternal family as a child

437
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:13,279
was because her destiny

438
00:27:13,559 --> 00:27:14,640
was hindering

439
00:27:15,000 --> 00:27:16,799
her father's official career.

440
00:27:17,880 --> 00:27:19,720
I never believed that kind of talk,

441
00:27:20,480 --> 00:27:21,799
but when I think about it carefully...

442
00:27:22,440 --> 00:27:23,279
well, don't you know.

443
00:27:24,119 --> 00:27:24,880
Your father

444
00:27:25,200 --> 00:27:26,599
was demoted

445
00:27:26,599 --> 00:27:27,880
and sent out to Pingyang Prefecture.

446
00:27:28,519 --> 00:27:29,839
Now her uncle

447
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:31,400
has been dismissed as well.

448
00:27:32,079 --> 00:27:33,039
Could it be that

449
00:27:33,279 --> 00:27:34,519
this fate business

450
00:27:34,920 --> 00:27:36,400
actually holds some truth?

451
00:27:37,680 --> 00:27:38,720
Mrs. Chen,

452
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:40,640
you'd better be careful.

453
00:27:40,960 --> 00:27:43,359
Your father and uncle are one thing,

454
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:45,920
but if it affects your husband...

455
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:51,519
Why bring all this up?

456
00:27:53,640 --> 00:27:55,160
I'm just kidding.

457
00:27:59,160 --> 00:28:00,000
Mrs. Wang is clearly

458
00:28:00,000 --> 00:28:01,759
trying to stir up trouble today.

459
00:28:02,160 --> 00:28:03,599
She's got grievances.

460
00:28:04,559 --> 00:28:06,160
The investigation into the Gu Deyuan case

461
00:28:06,480 --> 00:28:07,599
has dragged in over thirty

462
00:28:07,599 --> 00:28:08,839
court officials,

463
00:28:09,519 --> 00:28:10,559
yet not a single thread

464
00:28:10,799 --> 00:28:11,400
has linked

465
00:28:11,400 --> 00:28:12,799
to Chen Yanyun.

466
00:28:13,440 --> 00:28:15,000
Instead, the evidence of Wang Xuanfan

467
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:16,680
colluding with the late Prince Chengqing

468
00:28:16,839 --> 00:28:18,160
grows stronger by the day.

469
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:20,400
I heard the family of
that dead concubine

470
00:28:21,359 --> 00:28:22,839
has been found.

471
00:28:27,680 --> 00:28:28,319
Miss.

472
00:28:30,960 --> 00:28:31,519
Miss.

473
00:28:32,960 --> 00:28:33,559
What's wrong?

474
00:28:34,480 --> 00:28:35,400
Mr. Chen was

475
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:36,759
ambushed while inspecting

476
00:28:37,079 --> 00:28:37,920
Dingling at Yushan.

477
00:28:46,680 --> 00:28:47,240
Miss!

478
00:28:50,680 --> 00:28:52,279
I told you.

479
00:28:58,400 --> 00:28:59,000
What are you doing?

480
00:29:01,240 --> 00:29:01,720
You!

481
00:29:04,079 --> 00:29:05,640
If my husband

482
00:29:05,799 --> 00:29:07,319
had come to any harm today,

483
00:29:08,000 --> 00:29:09,119
I would hold you

484
00:29:09,319 --> 00:29:10,640
entirely responsible

485
00:29:11,160 --> 00:29:12,440
and make you pay with your life.

486
00:29:47,319 --> 00:29:48,039
Ma'am.

487
00:29:52,599 --> 00:29:53,759
It's my fault.

488
00:29:54,440 --> 00:29:55,440
I failed to protect him.

489
00:29:55,720 --> 00:29:56,960
Please punish me.

490
00:30:09,799 --> 00:30:10,319
My lady.

491
00:30:32,400 --> 00:30:32,920
Mother.

492
00:30:33,400 --> 00:30:34,559
Let's head back.

493
00:30:35,279 --> 00:30:36,680
Let Jinzhao stay with Yanyun.

494
00:30:46,759 --> 00:30:48,279
Why are his hands so cold?

495
00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:53,680
Yanyun.

496
00:30:58,720 --> 00:30:59,720
He left in a hurry

497
00:30:59,960 --> 00:31:01,359
and took only me with him.

498
00:31:02,279 --> 00:31:03,960
We hadn't gone far out of the capital

499
00:31:04,440 --> 00:31:05,480
when we ran into assassins.

500
00:31:06,319 --> 00:31:07,359
They outnumbered us

501
00:31:08,039 --> 00:31:09,839
and had crossbowmen hidden in the woods.

502
00:31:13,119 --> 00:31:14,160
Do you have any suspects?

503
00:31:15,039 --> 00:31:15,680
Yes.

504
00:31:17,279 --> 00:31:18,920
The court and the streets

505
00:31:20,559 --> 00:31:21,880
are all saying Wang Xuanfan, having been

506
00:31:22,319 --> 00:31:23,759
caught evidence against by Yanyun,

507
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:26,039
got desperate enough

508
00:31:27,519 --> 00:31:28,799
to hire killers to get rid of him.

509
00:31:33,480 --> 00:31:35,920
I did not assassinate him!

510
00:31:36,400 --> 00:31:36,920
Sir.

511
00:31:38,680 --> 00:31:40,000
Wang Shenzhi, the Chief Justice of

512
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:40,880
the Court of

513
00:31:41,079 --> 00:31:42,160
Judicial Review, is here

514
00:31:42,160 --> 00:31:43,400
to ask about the day

515
00:31:43,640 --> 00:31:44,720
Chen Yanyun was attacked.

516
00:31:45,640 --> 00:31:46,680
Go tell him

517
00:31:47,160 --> 00:31:48,240
I don't know who

518
00:31:48,240 --> 00:31:49,279
assassinated Chen Yanyun,

519
00:31:49,279 --> 00:31:51,000
but it certainly wasn't me!

520
00:31:51,440 --> 00:31:52,240
Exactly!

521
00:31:52,759 --> 00:31:53,799
Does he have evidence to

522
00:31:53,920 --> 00:31:54,960
just come and interrogate?

523
00:31:55,240 --> 00:31:56,160
It sounds like

524
00:31:56,440 --> 00:31:57,160
he does.

525
00:31:58,240 --> 00:31:58,960
I just

526
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:00,319
got word myself.

527
00:32:00,640 --> 00:32:01,319
One of the men

528
00:32:01,319 --> 00:32:02,400
we sent to tail Chen Yanyun

529
00:32:02,680 --> 00:32:03,640
has gone missing.

530
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:09,880
You may go now.

531
00:32:10,079 --> 00:32:10,559
Yes, ma'am.

532
00:32:20,519 --> 00:32:21,720
Why are you looking at me like that?

533
00:32:22,920 --> 00:32:23,880
Tell me the truth.

534
00:32:24,559 --> 00:32:25,519
Was it you or not?

535
00:32:26,039 --> 00:32:27,880
It really wasn't me!

536
00:32:30,240 --> 00:32:30,720
Yes,

537
00:32:31,279 --> 00:32:33,240
I'd love to kill him,

538
00:32:33,759 --> 00:32:35,680
but that would be rule-breaking.

539
00:32:35,880 --> 00:32:37,119
A Grand Secretary assassinating

540
00:32:37,119 --> 00:32:38,519
his college? It never happened!

541
00:32:40,119 --> 00:32:41,519
But people are saying

542
00:32:42,039 --> 00:32:43,759
that you, afraid Chen will reveal

543
00:32:43,759 --> 00:32:45,279
your collusion with Prince Chengqing,

544
00:32:45,839 --> 00:32:46,839
got desperate

545
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:48,039
and hired assassins.

546
00:32:48,039 --> 00:32:49,599
How can you say that?

547
00:32:49,880 --> 00:32:50,279
I...

548
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:56,559
People?

549
00:33:00,160 --> 00:33:00,839
No way.

550
00:33:02,119 --> 00:33:03,240
That's someone setting me up.

551
00:33:05,119 --> 00:33:05,680
Yes.

552
00:33:06,279 --> 00:33:06,640
Definitely,

553
00:33:07,240 --> 00:33:08,720
someone is setting me up.

554
00:33:08,759 --> 00:33:10,359
Who would dare set you up?

555
00:33:10,799 --> 00:33:11,359
Chen Yanyun.

556
00:33:12,640 --> 00:33:14,079
I've asked around.

557
00:33:14,400 --> 00:33:15,880
He really took an arrow,

558
00:33:16,359 --> 00:33:17,400
and it's pretty bad.

559
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:25,839
Do you think

560
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:28,480
it might be

561
00:33:29,160 --> 00:33:30,440
the Lord Chief Councilor?

562
00:33:34,799 --> 00:33:35,480
No way,

563
00:33:36,359 --> 00:33:37,200
absolutely impossible.

564
00:33:37,400 --> 00:33:38,599
He still needs me.

565
00:33:39,119 --> 00:33:39,960
He will protect me.

566
00:33:41,200 --> 00:33:42,480
Chen Yanyun's tricks

567
00:33:43,000 --> 00:33:43,519
are useless,

568
00:33:44,200 --> 00:33:45,079
definitely useless.

569
00:34:55,639 --> 00:34:57,320
Why the tears?

570
00:35:08,840 --> 00:35:09,679
Relax,

571
00:35:11,320 --> 00:35:12,320
I'm not dying.

572
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:20,440
How can I relax?

573
00:35:21,239 --> 00:35:22,559
You've lost so much blood

574
00:35:22,800 --> 00:35:24,079
and stayed unconscious.

575
00:35:24,840 --> 00:35:26,679
I've never seen you like this.

576
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:28,320
Don't ever

577
00:35:28,599 --> 00:35:29,960
scare me like that again.

578
00:35:35,199 --> 00:35:36,599
How do you feel now?

579
00:35:38,159 --> 00:35:39,119
Better.

580
00:35:43,519 --> 00:35:44,599
Then rest.

581
00:35:45,519 --> 00:35:46,360
I won't disturb you.

582
00:35:47,360 --> 00:35:48,119
Come back.

583
00:35:58,639 --> 00:35:59,239
Sit.

584
00:36:00,039 --> 00:36:00,719
I won't.

585
00:36:01,519 --> 00:36:02,440
Just say what you have to say.

586
00:36:06,719 --> 00:36:08,119
Why are you so stubborn?

587
00:36:08,760 --> 00:36:09,679
Because of you.

588
00:36:12,079 --> 00:36:13,960
