647
00:39:15,760 --> 00:39:16,239
Sir.

648
00:39:18,880 --> 00:39:19,719
What?

649
00:39:20,119 --> 00:39:20,920
Based on the clues
we left, the Court

650
00:39:22,039 --> 00:39:23,119
