657
00:39:34,159 --> 00:39:35,039
Then we just wait

658
00:39:35,960 --> 00:39:37,079
and see how things unfold.

659
00:39:37,480 --> 00:39:37,920
Yes, sir.

660
00:39:40,280 --> 00:39:41,039
What?

661
00:39:41,840 --> 00:39:43,039
Is Wang Xuanfan really

662
00:39:43,239 --> 00:39:44,440
behind this assassination?

663
00:39:44,639 --> 00:39:47,119
Truth and falsehood, interwoven—only then can one

664
00:39:48,280 --> 00:39:49,440
make it impossible for others

665
