696
00:41:12,079 --> 00:41:12,760
It hurts.

697
00:41:13,480 --> 00:41:14,000
It hurts.

698
00:41:15,440 --> 00:41:16,360
Hurting again?

699
00:41:18,760 --> 00:41:19,679
It hurts.

700
00:41:23,280 --> 00:41:24,719
