Then I'll go write the prescription.

714
00:42:23,639 --> 00:42:24,360
Please follow me.

715
00:42:41,039 --> 00:42:41,679
It's okay.

716
00:42:41,880 --> 00:42:42,760
Please have a seat, sir.

717
00:42:45,639 --> 00:42:46,719
When it comes to treating

718
00:42:47,159 --> 00:42:48,519
